<h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);color:var(--text-primary);">Laminate Flooring Installation</h2>

<p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);">Laminate flooring gives you the beauty of hardwood or stone at a fraction of the cost. Today's laminate products feature incredibly realistic textures and patterns — many homeowners can't tell the difference from real wood. Ake installs laminate with the same precision and care as any flooring type.</p>

<p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);">Laminate is an excellent choice for homeowners across the Mid-Willamette Valley who want beautiful, durable floors on a budget. It's quick to install, easy to maintain, and comes in a wide range of styles.</p>

<h3 style="font-size:var(--text-lg);font-weight:600;color:var(--text-primary);margin-top:var(--space-2xl);margin-bottom:var(--space-md);">Benefits of Laminate Flooring</h3>
<ul style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:2;padding-left:var(--space-lg);">
  <li><strong>Affordable</strong> — Significantly less expensive than hardwood</li>
  <li><strong>Durable</strong> — Scratch-resistant, fade-resistant, and impact-resistant</li>
  <li><strong>Quick Installation</strong> — Click-lock system means faster project completion</li>
  <li><strong>Low Maintenance</strong> — Sweep and damp mop is all you need</li>
  <li><strong>Realistic Looks</strong> — Wood, stone, and tile patterns with embossed textures</li>
  <li><strong>DIY-Unfriendly Details</strong> — Professional install ensures proper expansion gaps, transitions, and subfloor prep that prevent costly mistakes</li>
</ul>

